Package org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.server

Interface HasSubordinatesVirtualAttributeCfg

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Configuration, VirtualAttributeCfg
    public interface HasSubordinatesVirtualAttributeCfg
extends VirtualAttributeCfg
    A server-side interface for querying Has Subordinates Virtual Attribute settings.

    The Has Subordinates Virtual Attribute generates a virtual attribute that indicates whether the entry has any subordinate entries.
